{"id": 486, "genre": 1001, "title": "在这个时代如何做一个体面的好人？", "description": "我，汗我森上的每一个细胞，都在大森地缩，求放过！", "record_count": 3117, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130029M17DiLPQlVWv9UOB.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-08-18T14:45:13Z", "options": [{"id": 8452, "content": "遇人待事别太抠门儿，别炫富，富人多的是好吗好吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164011}, {"id": 18439, "content": "为了你我都忍着", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259101}, {"id": 9224, "content": "事情做了就别抱怨 既然抱怨了就甭去做", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169453}, {"id": 8723, "content": "有求必应", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166731}, {"id": 8470, "content": "好的。呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164223}, {"id": 8472, "content": "告别单身", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164207}, {"id": 8475, "content": "抬高自己的同时不要以贬低别人为基点", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164268}, {"id": 9245, "content": "静静的读本书（纸质那种）", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182837OaV4MgmNvxep5Ur9.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147245}, {"id": 8499, "content": "不给他人添麻烦，别给自己找麻烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163731}, {"id": 13630, "content": " 说实话", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209608}, {"id": 8258, "content": "不整天在朋友圈里秀娃", "image": null, "praise_count": 167, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 8259, "content": "取得同意再蹭隔壁WiFi", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 8260, "content": "抢红包也发红包", "image": null, "praise_count": 198, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 8516, "content": "心灵鸡汤属于转基因食品", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164609}, {"id": 8530, "content": "行胜于言，三思而动", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164850}, {"id": 8793, "content": "今天的我，胜过昨日的我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166429}, {"id": 8796, "content": "做个体面的坏人比较容易", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 97452}, {"id": 8817, "content": "好好说话，换位思考", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167748}, {"id": 9087, "content": "有钱，自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169069}, {"id": 8325, "content": "不要各种求投票，特别是给隔壁王大妈孙子的老师投票这种", "image": null, "praise_count": 265, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218}, {"id": 8326, "content": "不要秀恩爱不要秀恩爱不要秀恩爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 153, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113378}, {"id": 8329, "content": "她们都说我是好人", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 39258}, {"id": 8330, "content": "凭什么婚前就这么欺负人！", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 50350}, {"id": 8331, "content": "和朋友聊天的时候不要一个劲儿地看手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 339, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218}, {"id": 8332, "content": "不要各种角度拍照，拍到食物凉了才让人动筷子", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218}, {"id": 8333, "content": "不要在晒合照的时候把自己美美的别人丑丑的那张贴出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 143, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218}, {"id": 8589, "content": "不要每天发自拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164240}, {"id": 8335, "content": "有求于人时反复斟酌后再开口\n别人有难时、尽可能的帮忙", "image": null, "praise_count": 238, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162768}, {"id": 8336, "content": "己所不欲勿施于人", "image": null, "praise_count": 214, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 60125}, {"id": 8337, "content": "为人大方得体就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 92, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135605}, {"id": 8338, "content": "梦想尽在掌握，纯简随心，如玉凝成。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161501}, {"id": 8339, "content": "别各种求赞 求赏", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 8340, "content": "把自己打理好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 85, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 8341, "content": "男人就去做男闺蜜，女人就当好女神。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 11774}, {"id": 8597, "content": "不ཻ要ཻ装ཻ逼ཻ，坚ཻ持ཻ梦ཻ想ཻ，总ཻ有ཻ一ཻ天ཻ你ཻ会ཻ体ཻ面ཻ的ཻ生ཻ活ཻ", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 165216}, {"id": 8342, "content": "勇敢做自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157909}, {"id": 8343, "content": "体面容易，好人难做", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141699}, {"id": 8601, "content": "要大度，能容忍，不算计别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 165442}, {"id": 8347, "content": "有钱最体面", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146403}, {"id": 8350, "content": "拒绝直男癌，拒绝隐私透明", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155909}, {"id": 8362, "content": "学校就该毁灭，人们如同圈养的羔羊吃着腐朽的枯草。知识就是电离子，得到它们就像在空气中呼吸一样简单。", "image": "img/option/option/201607021829115Yd3PgWucVTyvq2Q.jpg", "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162857}, {"id": 8363, "content": "多拿好人卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 55088}, {"id": 8364, "content": "多挣钱，少炫富", "image": null, "praise_count": 85, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 86767}, {"id": 8365, "content": "明明...还是....", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158419}, {"id": 8367, "content": "做最真实的自己！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162909}, {"id": 8368, "content": "保持微笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 105318}, {"id": 8369, "content": "装逼可以，但不要太过分", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159942}, {"id": 8371, "content": "走路不要玩手机（ingress除外", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 21033}, {"id": 8372, "content": "懂得接受别人，但又不失原则", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147490}, {"id": 8374, "content": "别（朋友圈）提醒 过什么节日 本来不应该记住的 农历算什么东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}]}